--Added by Xanthus 7/16/99 5:25--<BR>
You get the Lense from the Named Evil Eye named Borxx In Runneye. He is Aprox. Level 30, and you would probably need at least 3 level 31 or higher. It would be better to use wizards or any type of high damage class becuase you want broxx dead quick-- He will charm. Take the lense to a Gnome in steamfont, I dont know the name, I believe we already have the quest, or part of it in the Quest section. Anyways, chat with the gnome for a bit and give him/her the lense. He/she will give the staff in return.<BR>
