			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			I have camped Borxx with a group of six people for about 5 hours. During that time he spawned about 5 times. First thing, DO NOT camp in the king room. Borxx is very anti-camp and he will rarly if ever spawn with you, camping in the king room. You probably know that he does spawn right next to the king spawn. What I did was we camped in the hallway outside the kingroom. (Its the hallway heading towards to Lord spawn room). We even had the king spawn 3 times in a row! Good luck with camping Borxx!
